### Genfeed API - Agent Thread Runtime Endpoints
### Canonical namespace: /agent/threads.

########################################
# Thread Runtime State
########################################

### Get Thread Snapshot
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/snapshot
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### List Thread Events
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/events?afterSequence=0
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Thread Interactions
########################################

### Respond To Pending Input Request
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/input-requests/{{testAgentInputRequestId}}/responses
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "answer": "Use the recommended option."
}


### Respond To UI Action
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/ui-actions
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "confirm_install_official_workflow",
  "payload": {
    "sourceId": "{{testWorkflowTemplateId}}"
  }
}


### Branch Thread
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/agent/threads/{{testAgentThreadId}}/branches
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
